      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 46.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天下有道，卻走馬以糞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When the Dao prevails in the world, they send back their swift horses to (draw) the dung- carts.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
