      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 46.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天下無道，戎馬生於郊。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When the Dao is disregarded in the world, the war-horses breed in the border lands.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
