      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 46.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>故知足之足，常足矣。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Therefore the sufficiency of contentment is an enduring and unchanging sufficiency.</seg>
